title: Media General, ABC Network Renew Affiliate Agreement
text:
Media General Inc. said it renewed its affiliate agreement with ABC Television Network.
Richmond, Va.-based Media General said the accord includes its expanded ABC television station portfolio under a common long-term agreement set to expire in 2021.
